  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have learned to enforce your will on your Sealed Beast. Your body has a much easier time pushing back its chakra and repairing itself. When you would complete a Long Rest, reduce the amount of Seal Bleed you have by 1. When you would spend Downtime to reduce your Seal Bleed, you reduce it by an additional 1d4. If you succeed a Bargain or Withdraw check by 10 or more and receive at least 10 Batches of Twisted Chakra, you also reduce the amount of Seal Bleed you would gain from this attempt by 1.</p>",
